teamhrupek2009 wrote a review Aug 2018
Osan, South Korea1 contribution
Better than expected!
We stayed with 3 small children under the age of 5 and were hoping to have enough space for everyone to relax. The room was very nice and had plenty of space for everyone to stretch out and still leave open areas after kids went to sleep. The staff was always very friendly and worked with us to make sure we had everything we wanted and needed. The restaurant had great food and lots of western options which was a surprise to my family after many travels throughout Asia. The pool and rooftop bar were very nice, as was the spa. The kids areas were very nice as well, we didn’t know what to expect honestly, they were small but the children loved them, good for kids below about 7 yrs old. Wish we could’ve stayed longer!
Dear teamhrupek2009, Thank you for taking the time to share your experience and post such a wonderful review. We truly appreciate your positive comments and compliments about our staff, the room, the beach and the food. We are glad that you had enjoyed your stay with us. We look forward to welcoming you back again soon. Kind regards, À La Carte Team.
