Dear Trâm N, Thank you for choosing to stay with us and taking the time to write a wonderful review. We are delighted to read your kind words about our hotel design, our breakfast buffet and our sea view. Look forward to welcoming you back soon. Kind regards, À La Carte Team.
LWilson1125 wrote a review Aug 2018
Singapore, Singapore65 contributions44 helpful votes
Chinese is everywhere
Like what stated in title, you will see Chinese people every corner in the hotel, especially at the lobby. They are just so noisy. Location: 10/10 (opposite to the sea) Environment: 3/10 (so noisy, just so noisy, kids running outside and you hear their footsteps like King Kong) Service: 8/10 (I will give them 10/10 if they can control the kids and even the customers) Food: 8/10 (room service with good western food at reasonable prices)
Responded Aug 20, 2018
Dear LWilson1125, Thank you so much for taking the time to write a review about our hotel, your feedback is very valuable to us. On behalf of Hotel Management, we are very regret to know that you had unpleasant experience during your stay with us due to the noise. However, we are glad that you enjoyed the location, the food and our service. Once again we do apologized for this inconvenience caused to you. Hopefully, we will have a chance to welcome you to our hotel again. Best regards, À La Carte Team
Matt_Hobbs wrote a review Aug 2018
Merseyside, United Kingdom28 contributions2 helpful votes
Comfortable and Convenient!
Stayed for a week with my girlfriend whilst visiting Da Nang and surrounding areas. The rooms are very spacious and comfortable, with great facilities and cleaning service. The staff were very helpful answering queries and providing a shuttle bus service to Hoi An, Ba Na Hills and the airport. The hotel is close to the beach, and there is a lovely view of it from the top (though currently there is a construction site on one side is slightly obstructive). The roof top pool and bar are a bonus for the view - especially at night! Hope to return again in the future.
Responded Aug 19, 2018
Dear Matt_Hobbs, We would like to express our appreciation to you for taking time to send us your feedback regarding your stay at À La Carte Danang Beach. We are delighted to know that you had wonderful time with your stay, your generous comments will be shared with our team and this feedback will serve as an encouragement to all of our staff as we strive to continuously improve the quality of our services. It is our pleasure of hosting you as our guest and hopefully, we would have opportunity to be at your service again in the future. Warm regards, À La Carte Team
